{"tid":779263,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人知呢套動畫咩名","createTime":"2018-08-14T09:39:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T10:38:59.000Z","uid":58462,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b6f75fb42317445a5dfd154ba7828498e81d0937","tid":779263,"uid":58462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:39:53.000Z","msg":"個故事設定係話軸心國贏咗二戰，日本同德國瓜分咗俄羅斯。之後德國侵略埋意大利，同日本陷入冷戰，最後兩國爆發戰爭。<br />\n第一集一開始係有兩三架日本戰機升空，啲戰機係好似火箭咁推進，機上裝咗坦克炮。睇到呢度冇睇落去了<br />\n<br />\n好耐之前download 咗打算睇，點知down完先發現冇中字，嗰陣又未識日文。而家識聽少少打算睇返，又唔記得叫咩名。個畫風都幾舊下，有冇ching知呢套嘢咩名？"},{"pid":"a8cbfa0fd99b6586e7cf843eaee828be52c3cdea","tid":779263,"uid":53800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:58:12.000Z","msg":"紺碧艦隊?<br />\n<br />\n唔知啱唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2496a815e426c758c770b54148654ce02c1c71","tid":779263,"uid":58462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8cbfa0fd99b6586e7cf843eaee828be52c3cdea","tid":779263,"uid":53800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:58:12.000Z","msg":"紺碧艦隊?<br />\n<br />\n唔知啱唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T10:38:59.000Z","msg":"好似唔係"}]}